<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Sat, 13 Jul 2024 18:15:15 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>中国谴责美国涉藏争端法案，誓言捍卫自身利益</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-blasts-us-tibet-china-dispute-bill-vows-defend-its-interests-2024-07-13/</link><description>中国周六对美国总统乔·拜登签署的一项美国法律表示强烈反对，该法律敦促北京解决西藏要求更大自治权的争端，并誓言“坚定捍卫”其利益。</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Jul 2024 09:45:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-blasts-us-tibet-china-dispute-bill-vows-defend-its-interests-2024-07-13/</guid></item><item><title>官方媒体称机构抢购中国国债正在做空经济</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/institutions-snapping-up-chinese-treasury-bonds-are-shorting-economy-state-media-2024-07-13/</link><description>中国央行支持的《金融时报》周六援引行业消息人士和专家的观点报道称，金融机构抢购中国国债基本上是在做空中国经济。</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Jul 2024 08:02:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/institutions-snapping-up-chinese-treasury-bonds-are-shorting-economy-state-media-2024-07-13/</guid></item><item><title>商务部副部长会见沃尔玛首席执行官麦克雷</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/chinas-vice-commerce-ministry-meets-walmart-ceo-mclay-2024-07-13/</link><description>中国商务部在一份声明中称，中国商务部副部长王受文周五会见了沃尔玛公司首席执行官凯瑟琳·麦克莱。</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Jul 2024 06:42:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/chinas-vice-commerce-ministry-meets-walmart-ceo-mclay-2024-07-13/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾参议院下令逮捕因涉嫌与中国犯罪有关的市长</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippine-senate-orders-arrest-mayor-probed-alleged-chinese-crime-ties-2024-07-13/</link><description>菲律宾参议院下令逮捕一名小镇市长，因为她拒绝出席调查她涉嫌与中国犯罪集团关系的听证会，该案在马尼拉和北京之间的紧张关系中引起了全国的关注。</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Jul 2024 05:39:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippine-senate-orders-arrest-mayor-probed-alleged-chinese-crime-ties-2024-07-13/</guid></item><item><title>台湾对华北“一波又一波”导弹试验保持警惕</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-alert-over-waves-missile-tests-north-china-2024-07-13/</link><description>台湾国防部周六表示，正在监测中国最北部内蒙古地区进行的“一波又一波”导弹试验，其防空部队已处于戒备状态。</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Jul 2024 05:11:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-alert-over-waves-missile-tests-north-china-2024-07-13/</guid></item><item><title>伊朗佩泽什基安拒绝美国压力，赞扬俄罗斯和中国</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/irans-pezeshkian-rejects-us-pressure-praises-russia-china-2024-07-12/</link><description>当选总统马苏德·佩泽什基安在周六发表的一份声明中表示，美国应该意识到伊朗不会对压力做出回应，他在声明中还强调了伊朗与中国和俄罗斯的友谊。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 23:11:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/irans-pezeshkian-rejects-us-pressure-praises-russia-china-2024-07-12/</guid></item><item><title>ASOIF表示，对中国游泳运动员的调查可能会阻止美国举办未来的赛事</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/probe-chinese-swimmers-could-keep-us-hosting-future-events-asoif-says-2024-07-12/</link><description>国际夏季奥林匹克运动会协会 (ASOIF) 周五表示，美国执法部门对涉及 23 名中国游泳运动员的兴奋剂案件进行的调查可能会阻止美国主办未来的体育赛事。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 20:44:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/probe-chinese-swimmers-could-keep-us-hosting-future-events-asoif-says-2024-07-12/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，德国将在欧盟对中国电动汽车关税的投票中投弃权票</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/germany-set-abstain-vote-eu-tariffs-chinese-evs-sources-2024-07-12/</link><description>消息人士周五告诉路透社，德国将在欧盟成员国周一就对中国制造的电动汽车征收临时关税的投票中投弃权票，这是对布鲁塞尔里程碑式贸易案支持的首次考验。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 15:31:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/germany-set-abstain-vote-eu-tariffs-chinese-evs-sources-2024-07-12/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，数据中心运营商 Equinix 考虑出售香港资产的少数股权</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/data-centre-operator-equinix-mulls-minority-stake-sale-hong-kong-assets-sources-2024-07-12/</link><description>两位消息人士称，全球数据中心运营商 Equinix 正在考虑出售其香港设施的少数股权，资产估值约为 20 亿美元，以利用人工智能需求的蓬勃发展。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 11:34:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/data-centre-operator-equinix-mulls-minority-stake-sale-hong-kong-assets-sources-2024-07-12/</guid></item><item><title>报道称，意大利将向中国汽车制造商提供已停产的 Stellantis 品牌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/italy-offer-defunct-stellantis-brands-chinese-automakers-report-says-2024-07-12/</link><description>据《Il Sole 24 Ore》周五报道，意大利政府正在考虑通过法令接管 Stellantis 旗下已不复存在的汽车品牌，并将其提供给中国企业，以鼓励它们在意大利设厂。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 09:53:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/italy-offer-defunct-stellantis-brands-chinese-automakers-report-says-2024-07-12/</guid></item><item><title>中国6月新增银行贷款未达预期，部分货币指标创历史新低</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/china-june-new-bank-loans-miss-forecasts-some-money-gauges-hit-record-lows-2024-07-12/</link><description>6月份，中国银行贷款增幅低于预期，而一些关键货币指标创下历史新低，突显出在中国最高领导人准备开会制定长期政策目标之际，世界第二大经济体的需求疲软。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 09:50:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/china-june-new-bank-loans-miss-forecasts-some-money-gauges-hit-record-lows-2024-07-12/</guid></item><item><title>中国6月对俄罗斯出口增速较上月加快</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/chinas-june-exports-russia-rise-more-quickly-than-previous-month-2024-07-12/</link><description>海关周五数据显示，6月份中国对俄罗斯以人民币计价的出口同比增长4.76%，高于5月份0.92%的增速，但仍远低于年初两位数的出口增速。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 07:07:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/chinas-june-exports-russia-rise-more-quickly-than-previous-month-2024-07-12/</guid></item><item><title>台湾将从中正纪念堂撤走仪仗队</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-withdraw-honour-guards-chiang-kai-shek-memorial-2024-07-12/</link><description>文化部周五表示，台湾将撤回前领导人蒋介石纪念馆的军事仪仗队，作为结束“崇拜威权主义”持续努力的一部分。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 06:37:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-withdraw-honour-guards-chiang-kai-shek-memorial-2024-07-12/</guid></item><item><title>中国队在巴黎横扫金牌，重回乒乓球霸主地位</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/china-eye-return-table-tennis-dominance-with-golden-sweep-paris-2024-07-12/</link><description>中国乒乓球队在东京奥运会混双项目上惨败于日本队后，将迎战巴黎奥运会，以横扫金牌的方式重新确立在这项运动中的绝对统治地位。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 06:13:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/china-eye-return-table-tennis-dominance-with-golden-sweep-paris-2024-07-12/</guid></item><item><title>中国银行周一维持中期贷款利率不变</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-cbank-seen-holding-medium-term-lending-rate-steady-monday-2024-07-12/</link><description>路透调查显示，人们普遍预计中国央行周一将到期贷款展期时将维持中期利率不变，并从银行体系中抽走部分现金。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 06:01:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-cbank-seen-holding-medium-term-lending-rate-steady-monday-2024-07-12/</guid></item></channel></rss>